{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We always saw each other from time to time, every few weeks or so.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would-- they would come to see me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would come to see them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Diadia Petia, the commander, he was just like a father to me, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was really good.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I forgot to mention in the story-- my story-- when we came back to Stepan after the war, and my brothers were in the in the police, going after the Nazis that the German-- the Ukrainian Nazis that were killing our families-- killed.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I forgot to mention that we did get a hold of the man that took my mother and me and took her to the police station.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did find this guy, and this guy was tried and sentenced.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Also, when my brother Chaim was killed, Yakov, my brother, was in the police, and he was very upset at that time.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he went into the village where he was killed and there were bandits called [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Malinsk ?] in that village.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he was-- really, got drunk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he took a machine gun and attacked the whole village, unfortunately, and killed a lot of people there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Soviet authorities put him to jail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was in jail and Diadia Petia became the Chief Justice in Rovno, in the city of Rovno, at that time, which was-- Rovno was the main city of the [NONENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SIGHS] And I was in such good terms with Diadia Petia that I was able to go to him.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was-- from school, I went to see Diadia Petia and asked him if he could release my brother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He says, it's very difficult what he did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I said, look.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The rage he was in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They killed my brother.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
